@{jcenter}Welcome to the Convertor 2.80 Guide! guide version 2.8.0 (21.09.99)
@{jleft}

I've split this guide into four main parts.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{u}@{fg shine}Introduction:@{uu}@{fg text} You have to read this whole part, very important topics are discussed here.

    @{"Postcardware" link "postcardware"}            Send me a postcard now! :-)

    @{"Requirements" link "requirements"}            Trying to run Convertor from a C64 would result in a complete failure.

    @{"Installation" link "installation"}            Just copy Convertor somewhere.

    @{"Mui" link "Mui"}                     I used it to create Convertor.

    @{"SI/base/composed units" link "sbc"}  Learn what these strange words mean in Convertor.

    @{"Level/Difference units" link "ld"}  Two ways to convert temperatures between..

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{u}@{fg shine}Tutorial:@{uu}@{fg text} This contains some examples to use Convertor. Reading this would make you more powerful with Convertor.

    @{"Tour" link "tour"}                    A guided tour of the incredible functions of Convertor.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{u}@{fg shine}Reference:@{uu}@{fg text} If you want help on a precise subject, select the topic and read it.

    @{"Window" link "window"}                  Everything about the interface

    @{"Menus" link "menus"}                   Try to press the right mouse button and discover the hidden power of Convertor.

    @{"Troubleshooting / QTCBA" link "troubleshooting"}  Read that before mailing me

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{u}@{fg shine}Misc. topics:@{uu}@{fg text} These are less important subjects.

    @{"Past" link "history.txt/main"}                    I already did a lot of work ..

    @{"Future" link "Future"}               .. but I still have a lot to do.

    @{"Bugs" link "bugs"}                    The nightmare of every programmer.

    @{"Thanks" link "Thanks"}                  People that helped me to bring Convertor to life.

    @{"My Address" link "me"}              How to contact me..

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

